Implement Phase 53: Hybrid Plugin Integration Layer.
Create manifest-based architecture for Zeaz Platform to manage embedded and external plugins.
Provide:
- configs/plugins/repositories.schema.json
- scripts/plugins/plugin-lib.sh
- scripts/plugins/plugin-list.sh
- scripts/plugins/plugin-validate.sh
- scripts/plugins/plugin-sync.sh
- scripts/plugins/plugin-health.sh
- scripts/plugins/plugin-render-cloudflare.sh
- scripts/plugins/plugin-evidence.sh

Follow rules:
- No hardcoded secrets.
- Dry run defaults.
- Do not mutate Cloudflare unless APPLY=true.
- Do not delete external repos.
- Cost lock requires true for paid CF features.
